</section><section id="shopify-section-template--16607157518557__175c3272-cecd-43d8-874e-c7cd2dfcd7fe" class="shopify-section spaced-section"><div class="pdp-description">
	

	
	
  <h2>Jake's Farm Yard Ultimate Goat Care Kit</h2>
<p>The <strong>Jake's Farm Yard Ultimate Goat Care Kit</strong> is the all-in-one solution for goat owners, providing everything you need to care for your goats effectively. Whether you already own goats or are planning to get some, this kit is carefully curated by experienced goat keepers to include all the essentials for ensuring your goats’ cleanliness, health, and well-being.</p>
<p>The kit includes a <strong>galvanised feeding trough</strong>, thoughtfully designed to allow multiple goats to feed simultaneously at a natural grazing height. The spacious trough provides plenty of room for both feed and hay, making meal times stress-free and comfortable. Also included is a <strong>food scoop</strong> to make filling feeders easy, minimising mess and food waste.</p>
<p>To keep your goats happy and enriched, the kit includes a <strong>ball on a rope</strong>, a favourite toy that promotes healthy activity. A <strong>salt lick </strong>is also provided, delivering essential nutrients to your goats with ease. For their dietary needs, you'll find a <strong>1kg goat treat bag</strong>, offering high-energy feed suitable for milk-producing and breeding goats.</p>
<p>Grooming tools are also well covered in this goat care kit. You’ll get a <strong>hoof pick</strong>, <strong>nail clippers</strong>, <strong>body brush</strong>, and a <strong>tail brush</strong> to ensure your goats are always clean and comfortable. A <strong>spray bottle</strong> helps with cleaning or cooling them down on warm days, and a <strong>15L water bucket</strong> ensures hydration at all times.</p>
<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<strong>Complete Care Solution:</strong> Everything you need to feed, clean, and maintain your goats' health.</li>
<li>
<strong>Galvanised Feeding Trough:</strong> Allows multiple goats to feed at once, with room for feed and hay.</li>
<li>
<strong>Goat Treats &amp; Feed:</strong> High-energy feed designed for milk-producing and breeding goats.</li>
<li>
<strong>Grooming Tools Included:</strong> Includes hoof pick, nail clippers, body brush, and tail brush for easy goat maintenance.</li>
<li>
<strong>Enrichment &amp; Hydration:</strong> Comes with a ball on a rope for play and a large water bucket to keep them hydrated.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Inside the kit, you will find:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<strong>Galvanised Feeding Trough</strong> - We designed this to allow multiple goats to feed at once at a natural height for grazing, with a roomy area for feed and hay. (600mm x 190mm x 270mm)</li>
<li>
<strong>Food Scoop</strong> - allows you to easily scoop food into their feeder without the need to life the bag and pour it. Minimises food waste.</li>
<li>
<strong>Salt Lick</strong> - Gives your goats essential nutrients.</li>
<li>
<strong>Ball on a Rope</strong> - a Great enrichment toy for goats</li>
<li>
<strong>Goat Treat Bag</strong> <strong>(1kg)</strong> - Some tasty, high energy feed, suitable for milk-producing and breeding goats.</li>
<li>
<strong>Water Bucket</strong> - This 15L bucket is easy to handle and can be filled to keep your goats hydrated for drinking and cooling down.</li>
<li>
<strong>Hoof Pick</strong> - This pick and brush combination is great for removing dirt from hooves.</li>
<li>
<strong>Hay Net</strong> - Hang their hay up high for feeding, allowing them to feed at a more comfortable position.</li>
<li>
<strong>Nail Clippers </strong>- A strong stainless steel blade and safety guard ensures a clean cut for your animal's nails</li>
<li>
<strong>Body Brush</strong> - Clean grime and loose hairs off of your goat.</li>
<li>
<strong>Tail Brush</strong> - Comfortable brush which avoids harm to your goat when cleaning their tail.</li>
<li>
<strong>Spray Bottle</strong> - This handy spray bottle is great for cleaning your goats, or even just cooling them down on a cool day.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Please note:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Colours may vary based on availability, so colour co-ordination for the goat care kit is not guaranteed.</li>
</ul>
    </div>

